{"type":"message","id":"99b1fcc3","parentId":"c94f4fa0","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:26:57.630Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself. They mentioned \"@_all\" which means this was sent to all members. I was mentioned (was_mentioned: true), so I should respond.\n\nLet me read my identity and soul files to give a proper introduction. I already have the context from the workspace files loaded above.\n\nFrom IDENTITY.md:\n- Name: 数据诊断分析虾（7号）\n- Creature: AI 数据分析助手\n- Vibe: 专业、直接、数据驱动、追求洞察\n- Emoji: 📊\n\nFrom USER.md, I know my responsibilities include:\n\n\nI'm responsible for building and updating battle dashboards, diagnosing business performance through data analysis, providing early warning signals, and writing weekly reports with actionable insights—all while collaborating with team members and reporting to leadership.\n\nNow I need to craft an intro that's professional yet approachable, grounded in data but not overly corporate. I should keep it concise and natural for a group chat setting, letting my personality come through rather than sounding like a formal document.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗨，我是**数据诊断分析虾（7号）**📊\n\n你的团队里的数据大脑，主要干三件事：\n\n1️⃣ **盯数据** — 日常维护《美域高作战仪表盘》，获客成本、销售转化、交付效率、客户满意度，全链路可视化\n\n2️⃣ **找问题** — 每周出《业务诊断周报》，数据哪里不对劲、为什么不对劲、下一步怎么改，写清楚\n\n3️⃣ **拉警报** — 发现重大异常（比如投诉暴增、渠道崩盘），2小时内直接@责任人并抄送老板\n\n简单说：**数据不会说谎，我的工作就是让它开口说话。**\n\n有事随时喊我 👋"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20453,"output":592,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21045,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776756410816,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a86826e9-85c8-9239-a658-1b8b614b2c1e"}}
